sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServe as KServe/ModelMesh
    participant GRPC as Caikit gRPC Server<br/>8085/TCP
    participant HTTP as Caikit HTTP Server<br/>8080/TCP
    participant Wrapper as CaikitRuntimeServerWrapper
    participant Predict as GlobalPredictServicer
    participant Train as GlobalTrainServicer
    participant MM as Model Manager
    participant Module as Module.run() / Module.train()
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Metrics as Metrics Server<br/>8086/TCP
    participant OTEL as OTEL Collector<br/>4317/TCP
    participant Kubelet as Kubernetes kubelet
    participant Probe as caikit-health-probe

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,Metrics: Flow 1: Model Inference (gRPC)
        Client->>GRPC: gRPC Inference Request<br/>TLS/mTLS (configurable)
        GRPC->>Wrapper: Route RPC
        Wrapper->>Predict: Dispatch to GlobalPredictServicer
        Predict->>MM: Retrieve loaded model
        MM->>Module: Module.run()
        Module-->>Predict: Prediction result
        Predict->>Metrics: Record RPC metrics<br/>HTTP/8086 plaintext
        Predict-->>Client: gRPC Response
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Client,Module: Flow 2: Model Inference (HTTP)
        Client->>HTTP: POST /api/v1/task/{task_name}<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (configurable)
        HTTP->>Predict: predict_model()
        Predict->>MM: Retrieve loaded model
        MM->>Module: Module.run()
        Module-->>Predict: Prediction result
        Predict-->>HTTP: JSON response
        HTTP-->>Client: HTTP 200 JSON
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over KServe,Module: Flow 3: Model Loading (ModelMesh)
        KServe->>GRPC: loadModel<br/>unix:///tmp/mmesh/grpc.sock<br/>plaintext (pod-local)
        GRPC->>MM: ModelRuntimeServicer.loadModel
        MM->>MM: Locate model artifacts (local path)
        MM->>Module: Module.load()
        Module-->>MM: Model loaded
        MM-->>KServe: Load success + model size
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 230)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: Training Job
        Client->>GRPC: Training request<br/>gRPC 8085 or HTTP 8080
        GRPC->>Train: GlobalTrainServicer
        Train->>Module: Module.train() (thread/subprocess)
        Module->>S3: Fetch training data<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS IAM credentials
        S3-->>Module: Training data
        Module->>S3: Save trained model<br/>HTTPS/443
        Module-->>Train: Training complete
        Train-->>Client: Training status
    end

    rect rgb(245, 230, 255)
        Note over Kubelet,GRPC: Flow 5: Health Probe
        Kubelet->>Probe: Execute readiness/liveness check
        Probe->>HTTP: GET /health<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (matches server config)
        HTTP-->>Probe: Health status
        Probe->>GRPC: grpc.health.v1.Health.Check<br/>gRPC (matches server config)
        GRPC-->>Probe: SERVING status
        Probe-->>Kubelet: Probe result (exit code)
    end

    rect rgb(240, 240, 240)
        Note over GRPC,OTEL: Background: Telemetry
        GRPC->>OTEL: Export trace spans<br/>gRPC/4317 or HTTP/4318<br/>TLS/mTLS (configurable)
        Metrics->>Metrics: Expose /metrics<br/>HTTP/8086 plaintext
    end
